flowchart TB
    Q[Query Node] --> R[Centroid routing]
    R --> LC[Light cone filter]
    LC --> P[Pad to fixed width<br/>with random authorized cells<br/>F-0.8 closed]
    P --> G[Group by owner / context]
    G --> FO{For each owner:<br/>try registered<br/>oracle endpoints<br/>in order}
    FO -->|endpoint 1| O1[Oracle replica 1]
    FO -->|on failure| O2[Oracle replica 2]
    FO -->|on failure| O3[Oracle replica 3]
    O1 --> TH[Threshold reconstruction<br/>SecureBytes wrapper<br/>zeroized in finally]
    TH --> TTL[Sign batch + TTL<br/>F-1.5 closed]
    TTL --> Q
    Q --> ENF[TTL re-check<br/>at use time]
    ENF --> DEC[Decrypt cells<br/>discard padded keys]
    DEC --> RANK[Merge + rank]
